00:31:51.940 --> 00:31:53.790
As opposed to you coming into
my office pulling your hair out,

00:31:53.790 --> 00:31:56.910
going, my wife's going to leave
me unless we move back east.

00:31:56.910 --> 00:31:58.960
Let's have that
discussion in advance.

00:31:58.960 --> 00:32:00.980
Where do you see
your family going?

00:32:00.980 --> 00:32:03.150
Are you getting a good
life work life integration.

00:32:03.150 --> 00:32:04.816
Not balance, because
there's no balance.

00:32:04.816 --> 00:32:06.897
There's an integration.

00:32:06.897 --> 00:32:08.480
You want to work at
