00:32:22.800 --> 00:32:24.000
Sure.

00:32:24.000 --> 00:32:25.420
Because that's important to you.

00:32:25.420 --> 00:32:27.720
And I'm invested in
you as a human being.

00:32:27.720 --> 00:32:29.900
I've got to make sure
