It's not professional.

00:32:39.870 --> 00:32:41.390
It's not your family.

00:32:41.390 --> 00:32:42.780
Whatever else you care about.

00:32:42.780 --> 00:32:44.050
What do you care about?

00:32:44.050 --> 00:32:46.692
So it could be I need
time to meditate.

00:32:46.692 --> 00:32:47.650
I want to take a class.

00:32:47.650 --> 00:32:49.816
I want to volunteer at my
kids' school twice a week.

00:32:50.655 --> 00:32:54.002
I'd like to get
involved in some-- I

00:32:54.002 --> 00:32:56.129
