00:37:10.130 --> 00:37:14.180
So if employees understand
that transcendent purpose,

00:37:14.180 --> 00:37:16.470
the neuroscience
suggests that there would

00:37:16.470 --> 00:37:17.910
be this synergistic effect.

00:37:17.910 --> 00:37:21.160
High trust plus high purpose
would produce this great sense

00:37:21.160 --> 00:37:22.390
of joy, this happiness.

00:37:22.390 --> 00:37:23.654
I just love it here.

