00:43:34.880 --> 00:43:35.420
Where are you going?

00:43:35.420 --> 00:43:36.128
What do you like?

00:43:36.128 --> 00:43:37.940
Which division would
you like to move to?

00:43:37.940 --> 00:43:41.020
How do I help you get your
next job within this company?

00:43:41.020 --> 00:43:43.350
So really, really effective.

00:43:43.350 --> 00:43:45.260
Communicate clearly the change.

00:43:45.260 --> 00:43:46.770
Implement the change.

00:43:46.770 --> 00:43:50.194
And in this company,
retention went way up.

00:43:50.194 --> 00:43:51.110
People said, oh, yeah.

00:43:51.110 --> 00:43:51.920
Now I get.

