00:48:14.459 --> 00:48:16.000
From my time here
today, I understand

00:48:16.000 --> 00:48:19.540
that you guys create
teams are very rapidly

00:48:19.540 --> 00:48:21.600
and reform teams very rapidly.

00:48:21.600 --> 00:48:23.152
So it's difficult
to trust someone

00:48:23.152 --> 00:48:24.360
