00:48:28.160 --> 00:48:28.951
How do I know that?

00:48:28.951 --> 00:48:30.280
How do I build trust rapidly?

00:48:30.280 --> 00:48:31.950
So that's what I
want to talk about.

00:48:31.950 --> 00:48:37.040
And one way is to use these
factors in the micro scale.

00:48:37.040 --> 00:48:41.630
So I can actually tell the
people in my group something

00:48:41.630 --> 00:48:42.630
vulnerable about myself.

00:48:42.630 --> 00:48:43.588
Something embarrassing.

00:48:43.588 --> 00:48:44.650
Something difficult.

00:48:44.650 --> 00:48:46.180
So I have students
do this in class.

00:48:46.180 --> 00:48:47.930
So tell me something
really weird about yourself

00:48:47.930 --> 00:48:48.804
so I can remember it.

00:48:48.804 --> 00:48:50.400
First, I'll remember you better.

00:48:50.400 --> 00:48:53.960
But something that's
not super flattering.

00:48:53.960 --> 00:48:55.126
Something unusual.

00:48:55.126 --> 00:48:56.250
So you can start with that.

00:48:56.250 --> 00:48:57.820
Just start small.

00:48:57.820 --> 00:49:00.080
Before we talk about
work, let's just about us.

00:49:00.080 --> 00:49:02.288
We're going to have to work
