00:50:04.750 --> 00:50:06.550
It's not focusing so much on me.

00:50:06.550 --> 00:50:08.060
Let's just focus on who you are.

00:50:08.060 --> 00:50:09.560
What do you want
to get out of this?

00:50:09.560 --> 00:50:10.750
What are your real goals?

00:50:10.750 --> 00:50:12.850
What drives you crazy here?

00:50:12.850 --> 00:50:15.090
What makes you super happy?

00:50:15.090 --> 00:50:17.320
We could do that in 10 minutes.

00:50:17.320 --> 00:50:19.680
Tell me one thing that's
really unusual that you

00:50:19.680 --> 00:50:21.920
love about Google,
