00:50:28.700 --> 00:50:31.600
So let me know about
you, because you're

00:50:31.600 --> 00:50:33.210
a human, not a human resource.

00:50:33.210 --> 00:50:37.674
So I think just changing
that language is a start.

00:50:37.674 --> 00:50:39.090
Are there personality
differences?

00:50:39.090 --> 00:50:39.670
For sure.

00:50:39.670 --> 00:50:42.340
And we see in experiments
