are super responders.

00:50:44.200 --> 00:50:50.060
They increase oxytocin
levels with a social stimulus

00:50:50.060 --> 00:50:52.290
five standard variations
above the mean.

00:50:52.290 --> 00:50:54.731
And they're super
empathic, super warm.

00:50:54.731 --> 00:50:55.980
Those people are always great.

00:50:55.980 --> 00:50:57.080
They have tons of friends.

00:50:57.080 --> 00:50:58.290
Everything works for them.

00:50:58.290 --> 00:51:00.373
What I think you want to
