00:51:02.140 --> 00:51:04.090
Who maybe are more introverted.

00:51:04.090 --> 00:51:06.642
Who don't like to leave
their offices much.

00:51:06.642 --> 00:51:09.100
Say, let's go down
to the cafeteria.

00:51:09.100 --> 00:51:11.930
Let's grab a coffee or
grab a beer after work.

00:51:11.930 --> 00:51:15.510
Spend a little bit of investment
and get to know that person.

00:51:15.510 --> 00:51:17.630
I think it's not that hard.

00:51:17.630 --> 00:51:20.720
And you know my prescription
