So it's OK.

00:51:23.600 --> 00:51:25.070
You can hug people at work.

00:51:25.070 --> 00:51:26.400
You won't get sued.

00:51:26.400 --> 00:51:28.467
No creepy hugs.

00:51:28.467 --> 00:51:30.300
Just say, look, I hug
everybody in my group.

00:51:30.300 --> 00:51:32.062
I saw a lot of
people hugging today.

00:51:32.062 --> 00:51:32.770
It's appropriate.

